com.rbmhtechnology.vind.api.query.facet

Class Facet.DateRangeFacet<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rbmhtechnology.vind.api.query.facet.Facet
      • com.rbmhtechnology.vind.api.query.facet.Facet.DateRangeFacet<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Spectated type of content from the field to be faceted.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Facet.DateRangeFacet.DateMathRangeFacet, Facet.DateRangeFacet.UtilDateRangeFacet, Facet.DateRangeFacet.ZoneDateRangeFacet
    Enclosing class:
    Facet

    public abstract static class Facet.DateRangeFacet<T>
extends Facet
    This abstract class provides the foundations to be implemented by date type specific classes in order to perform ranged facet query on a date field. A facet ranged query returns all the documents which have the specified field with a value included in a range defined by start and end. The result documents are faceted in the range steps of the size described by the property gap.
